# Wankr Backend: Always Use Infisical

**Never start the API with plain `npm start`.** The backend needs XAI_API_KEY from Infisical. Always use Infisical to inject secrets.

## Correct startup
- Use `start_backend.bat` (runs `infisical run --env=dev -- node wankr-backend/server.js`)
- The launcher (wankr.bat) must call `start_backend.bat`, not `npm start`

## When adding new launchers or scripts
- Any script that starts the Node backend must use Infisical via `start_backend.bat` or `infisical run -- node wankr-backend/server.js`
